name: DogeCoin To The Moon & Beyond
description:
Also available on iPhone & Android.

DogeCoins and DogeRocks rain down on you flying through space!
Collect DogeCoins and destroy DogeRocks to increase your score.

Collect PowerUps to gain advantages while in game.
Unlock: Paws, Heads, Feet, and Jet Packs to customize your player!

Thanks for playing, hope you have fun!
